Package: bc-vigil
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         python3 (>= 3.11),
         adduser
Recommends: bc-hash,
            bc-duplicate
Description: BitCrafts Vigil - file integrity monitoring web UI
 Web frontend for bc-hash. Lets operators register targets (file
 trees to hash), schedule periodic scans, and compare results to a
 baseline to detect file integrity drift (added / removed / modified).
 .
 Also ships a duplicate-file finder module backed by bc-duplicate:
 register trees, schedule periodic scans, and review duplicate
 groups with wasted-bytes accounting.
 .
 Includes a storage module showing disk usage per mountpoint, DB
 backup/restore/reset, and an FR/EN UI.
